name: Fit Pro Deals
tag_list: fitness, fitness-deals, fitness-trainer, personal-trainer, fitness-equipment, fitness-gear
overview:
Fit Pro Deals is a website that offers discounts on fitness gear, apparel, equipment, and business tools and software for fitness professionals.

As a Personal Trainer, Kris Crepeau became increasingly frustrated on how much money he was spending on fitness equipment for his studio. Kris soon found out that his frustrations were shared by many fitness professionals throughout the fitness industry, so he decided to launch a website to help out his fellow fitness pros.

FitProDeals.Com was launched in September of 2012 and is quickly becoming very popular in the fitness industry. Not only can you get great deals on fitness gear and equipment, but they also have a blog where successful fitness pros share their secrets to success.
